          # Existing project source (untouched)\n   590â†’â”śâ”€â”€ CLAUDE.md                 # Host CLAUDE.md\n   591â†’â””â”€â”€ .git/\n   592â†’```\n   593â†’\n   594â†’## Daemon Configuration\n   595â†’\n   596â†’| Variable | Default | Description |\n   597â†’|----------|---------|-------------|\n   598â†’| `CLOCHE_LISTEN` | `unix:///tmp/cloche.sock` | Listen address (unix socket or TCP) |\n   599â†’| `CLOCHE_DB` | `cloche.db` | SQLite database path |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9be06376-5a43-40f9-8380-030cf073c859","uuid":"a696b067-6d34-4c7f-9541-c8fe72705679","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","content":"3. Validation output from `.cloche/<run-id>/output/*.log` (output from previous script steps)\n4. Result selection instructions listing the step's declared results\n\n## Project Directory Layout\n\n```\nmy-project/\nâ”śâ”€â”€ .cloche/\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ develop.cloche        # Container workflow definition\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ host.cloche           # Host orchestration workflow (runs on host)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ Dockerfile            # Container image\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ config.toml           # Project configuration (orchestration, evolution)\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ prompts/\nâ”‚   â”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ implement.md      # Prompt templates\nâ”‚   â”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ fix.md\nâ”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ update-docs.md\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ scripts/\nâ”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ prepare-prompt.sh # Host-side prompt generation script\nâ”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ overrides/            # Files copied on top of /workspace/ in container\nâ”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ CLAUDE.md         # Container-specific CLAUDE.md (optional)\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ <run-id>/             # Runtime state (gitignored)\nâ”‚       â”śâ”€â”€ prompt.txt        # User prompt (from --prompt flag)\nâ”‚       â”śâ”€â”€ output/\nâ”‚       â”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ full.log      # Unified chronological log (status + script + LLM)\nâ”‚       â”‚   â”śâ”€â”€ test.log      # Per-step script output\nâ”‚       â”‚   â””â”€â”